rows.label: qst101403_msg001
rows.name:
Looks like him and herbivorous monsters
were attacked by other monsters (prov)

rows.label: qst101403_msg0001
rows.name:
Dead...
Bitten to death, looks like.

rows.label: qst101403_msg0002
rows.name: Here... See these prints?

rows.label: qst101403_msg0003
rows.name:
We can track them.
Let's go.

rows.label: qst101403_msg0004
rows.name: I could only follow them so far...

rows.label: qst101403_msg0101
rows.name:
Not breathing...
There's a bunch of bite marks.

rows.label: qst101403_msg0102
rows.name:
Huh?
I see prints.

rows.label: qst101403_msg0103
rows.name:
I can track 'em!
Let's go!

rows.label: qst101403_msg0104
rows.name: I don't think I can track 'em though...

rows.label: qst101403_msg0201
rows.name:
We're too late...
Something bit 'em to death.

rows.label: qst101403_msg0202
rows.name: Hm? Are those tracks?

rows.label: qst101403_msg0203
rows.name:
We can follow 'em,
see where they lead.

rows.label: qst101403_msg0204
rows.name:
Probably won't be able to follow
them, though...

rows.label: qst101403_msg0301
rows.name:
No heartbeat... Something go
munch-munch on body.

rows.label: qst101403_msg0302
rows.name:
Meh?
Tora find marks on ground!

rows.label: qst101403_msg0303
rows.name:
We can track tracks!
Follow quick!

rows.label: qst101403_msg0304
rows.name:
No good, meh...
Not able to track tracks very far...

rows.label: qst101403_msg0401
rows.name:
Dead...
Are those...bite marks?

rows.label: qst101403_msg0402
rows.name:
And there...
Tracks on the ground.

rows.label: qst101403_msg0403
rows.name: We should see where they lead us.

rows.label: qst101403_msg0404
rows.name:
But we won't be able to follow
all the way...
